(Massacra album)</a>, 1994</li> <li><a href="/wiki/Sick_(Sow_album)" title="Sick (Sow album)"><i>Sick</i> (Sow album)</a>, 1998</li> <li><a href="/wiki/Sick_(Loaded_album)" title="Sick (Loaded album)"><i>Sick</i> (Loaded album)</a>, 2009</li> <li><a href="/wiki/Sick_(EP)" title="Sick (EP)"><i>Sick</i> (EP)</a>, the 2013 debut release by American hardcore punk band Beartooth</li> <li><a href="/wiki/Sicks_(album)" title="Sicks (album)"><i>Sicks</i> (album)</a>, a 1986 album by Barnes &amp; Barnes</li> <li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Sicks&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Sicks (page does not exist)">The Sicks</a></i>, a 2001 EP by Majandra Delfino</li> </ul> <h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Songs">Songs</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Sick&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Songs">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3> <ul> <li><a href="/wiki/Sick_(song)" title="Sick (song)">"Sick" (song)</a>, a song by Adelitas Way</li> <li>"Sick", a song by Dope from <i><a href="/wiki/Felons_and_Revolutionaries" title="Felons and Revolutionaries">Felons and Revolutionaries</a></i></li> <li>"Sick", a song by Evanescence from <i><a href="/wiki/Evanescence_(Evanescence_album)" title="Evanescence (Evanescence album)">Evanescence</a></i></li> <li>"<a href="/wiki/Sick_(CeCe_Peniston_song)" title="Sick (CeCe Peniston song)">Sick</a>", a 2014 song by <a href="/wiki/CeCe_Peniston" title="CeCe Peniston">CeCe Peniston</a> featuring Paris Toon and Mother's Favorite Child</li> <li>"Sick", a 1997 song by <a href="/wiki/Green_Day" title="Green Day">Green Day</a></li> <li>The Sick, a Swedish band formed by two members of <a href="/wiki/Dozer" title="Dozer">Dozer</a></li> <li>"(sic)", a song by the American heavy metal band <a href="/wiki/Slipknot_(band)" title="Slipknot (band)">Slipknot</a></li> </ul> <h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Other_media">Othe